snippet.title: Inside A Mind
snippet.description:
Reality and fiction blends together more than you'd believe. Sometimes it can be praised. Other's can be looked upon in disgust.

This channel takes a dive into the strangest corners of the internet. Analysing how artists incorporate their work into reality, and how the public react to it.
